<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE topic PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Topic//EN" "topic.dtd">
<topic id="definition-lists">
  <title>Definition Lists</title>
  <body>
    <p>Definition lists are represented with table-like Word structures.</p>
    <dl id="definition-list">
      <dlentry>
        <dt>Ordered list</dt>
        <dd>
          <p>A list where item order is semantically meaningful.</p>
          <p>Continuation paragraph for definition-list indentation.</p>
        </dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>Bullet list</dt>
        <dd><p>A list where item order is not semantically meaningful.</p></dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>
  </body>
</topic>
